WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.360
Briefly about how we shot the vlog: after releasing our first full-length video,

2
00:00:04.360 --> 00:00:08.000
we decided to shoot a second one since we were happy with the result.

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.600
I called Nikita, and after that we started thinking about the project.

4
00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:16.560
We decided to create a plan to work from.

5
00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:21.200
Who would participate? What would we film? And so on.

6
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:26.000
Then Darina joined our project and agreed to appear in the video.

7
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.000
We decided that on January 15th at 2 o'clock we would meet at the institute and start filming.

8
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.000
But in the end, both Darina and I were late.

9
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:40.200
We were helped with filming by the guys from Sotsium: Pasha, who we interviewed,

10
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:45.200
shot almost all the footage, and Nikita, who managed the process.

11
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:48.200
Of course, there were plenty of failed takes.

12
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:49.200
And?

13
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.300
Well?

14
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:51.300
I thought you were going to say it.

15
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:55.200
A big thank you to Darina, as well as to Nikita and Pasha.

16
00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:59.400
Subscribe to Sotsium and Prodolzheniye, and also to the guys.

17
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:02.400
All contacts are listed in the description.
